Reigning Miss South Africa Ntandoyenkosi Kunene is getting ready to represent SA at the upcoming Miss World pageant in the US next month.The 23-year-old qualified teacher s departure to America has been kept under wraps with Miss SA organisers remaining tight-lipped on the exact departure date and her itinerary.Unlike the 65th edition of the Miss World pageant at the Crown of Beauty Theatre in Sanya, China, there will be no date clashes between the two major international beauty pageants.NONTOKOZO GXUMISA|nontokozog@thenewage.co.za